<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/55401ACNDTGGQPPPTRVGVMSDRVVBMKVVG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Season Finale Showcase";
  schema:description """
	Join us for an inspiring evening of dance as the talented performers of Studio North Dance Academy take the stage to celebrate a year of dedication, growth, and artistry. This annual year-end recital showcases dancers of all ages and levels in a vibrant collection of ballet, jazz, contemporary, lyrical, and more.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From our youngest rising stars to our senior performers, each piece highlights the passion, creativity, and hard work developed throughout the season. Audiences can expect an engaging and heartfelt performance that reflects the strong sense of community and excellence that defines Studio North.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come celebrate the joy of dance and support these incredible young artists as they shine on stage!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $33.00 Adult, $30.00 Student <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Babes in Arms:</span> Each person <span class=\"BoldText\">REGARDLESS OF AGE</span> must have a valid ticket to enter a performance. If you have an infant <span class=\"BoldText\">under the age of two</span> who will be sitting on your lap, please let our Box Office know and we will issue a complimentary ticket for your infant. All persons age two and up must have paid admission.</span>
""";
